<p>Different types of arithmetic systems are discussed in the academic lite=
rature. They differ from each other based on what type of number they opera=
te on, what numeral system they use to represent them, and whether they ope=
rate on mathematical objects other than numbers.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-67" cla=
