<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arithmetic#cite_note-75"><span cla=
ss=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>70<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></su=
p> Computer science is interested in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wi=
ki/Multiplication_algorithms" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Multiplication=
 algorithms">multiplication algorithms</a> with a low <a href=3D"https://en=
