xity">computational complexity</a> to be able to efficiently multiply very =
large integers, such as the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karats=
uba_algorithm" title=3D"Karatsuba algorithm">Karatsuba algorithm</a>, the <=
a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sch%C3%B6nhage%E2%80%93Strassen_alg=
orithm" title=3D"Sch=C3=B6nhage=E2=80=93Strassen algorithm">Sch=C3=B6nhage=
