 class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> Methods to calculate <a href=3D"=
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithm" title=3D"Logarithm">logarithms</a>=
 include the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taylor_series" title=
=3D"Taylor series">Taylor series</a> and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.or=
